Package mdxmlconverter.element

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert OwnedAttributes of a PackagedElement to an UmlAttribute and adds it to the corresponding UmlElement
    AttributeConverterTest
    Tests the AttributeConverter.
    DataTypeConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert strings representing data types or replaces the id of a PackagedElement with its name, if the datatype is a reference
    DataTypeConverterTest
    Tests the DataTypeConverter.
    ElementConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert PackagedElement to an UmlElement
    ElementConverterTest  
    LiteralConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert the OwnedLiterals of an PackagedElement of type 'uml:Enumeration' to UmlLiterals
    LiteralConverterTest
    Tests LiteralConverter
    ModifierConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert modifier information
    ModifierConverterTest
    Tests the methods of ModifierConverter.
    NestedElementConverter
    Class providing a method to convert an nested element of a PackagedElement and adds it to the owning UmlElement
    NestedElementConverterTest
    Tests the NestedElementConverter
    OperationConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert a given OwnedOperation to an UmlOperation and adds it to its UmlElement
    OperationConverterTest
    Tests OperationConverter.
    ParameterConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert OwnedParameters of an OwnedOperation to UmlParameters
    ParameterConverterTest
    Tests the ParameterConverter.
    ParameterDirectionConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert a string with information about the direction of a OwnedParameter to an UmlParameterDirection
    ParameterDirectionConverterTest
    Tests the method of ParameterDirectionConverter.
    TemplateBindingConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert TemplateBindings of PackagedElements and OwnedOperations to UmlTemplateBindings
    TemplateBindingConverterTest
    Tests the TemplateBindingConverter
    TemplateParameterConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert OwnedTemplateSignatures to UmlTemplateParameters
    TemplateParameterConverterTest
    Tests the TemplateParameterConverter.
